      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a simple way to get from A to B? This vehicle is in rough condition and will need some dedicated work to get it back to its best, but it's a fantastic opportunity for a mechanic or someone handy with cars! It's priced to move and ready for someone who sees the potential in a fixer-upper. Grab a bargain and make this car your next weekend project!",
