    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, representing the pinnacle of care and maintenance. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, showroom shine, and the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it performs perfectly; the engine is exceptionally smooth, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and every feature functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer seeking a vehicle that looks and drives like it just rolled off the assembly line.",
