    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a major project or a donor car for parts. The exterior has several significant dents, peeling clear coat, and visible rust spots along the wheel wells. Mechanically, the engine starts but runs roughly, and the suspension will need a complete overhaul to be safe for the road. The interior is heavily worn with cracked upholstery and some missing trim pieces.",
