    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit represents a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen in concours-level condition, exhibiting flawless paintwork and a pristine interior that remains indistinguishable from new. Mechanically, the vehicle has been subjected to rigorous inspection and service, ensuring performance that meets original factory specifications. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing short of perfection, this offering stands as a benchmark of its class.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
